\id 1TH Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 1THESSALONIKA
\toc1 1THESSALONIKA
\toc2 1Thessalonika
\toc3 1Th
\mt1 THESSALONIKA CAPAT
\mt3 A Pacuek Nah
\mt4 (First Letter to the Thessalonians)
\is2 THESSALONIKA CAPAT KAWNG
\im Paul loh Thessalonika hlang boel a pai sak (2.13,14) vaengah he amah loh bi mat a bi (2.9). Thessalonika he Greek tlangpuei ah olpuei khopuei la om. Kutsaii aka bawk he muep om dae Khrihca la boeih kun uh (1.9). Tedae amih te Boeipa dongah uepom la om uh tih amih kah olthang te paeng tom la yilhcet (1.8). Hekah capat he Olkhueh Thai khuiah lamhma cuek a tael la om coi ni.
\ip Thessalonika ah he Paul aka tloelh khaw bet om tih amah te Athens kho la vik cet. Te dongah cadong Timothy te a tueih tih Khrihca bu metla a om khaw duem a dongvoeng sak (3.1-5). Timothy a bal vaengah tah amih kah tangnah neh lungnah kawng te Paul ham olthangthen la a khuen pah (3.6-10).
\ip Hlangboel khuiah a lolhnah om. A ngen long tah Boeipa ha rhum pawn ni tila a poek tholh dongah bi aka bi mueh khaw om uh (4.11,12). A ngen bal tah Khrih a rhum hlan ah aka duek a huiko ham mawntangnah a khueh uh. Te dongah Paul loh Khrih a rhumnah kawng te cimphan la a thuicaih pah (4.13-15). Amih ham te tahae tue metlam kho n'sak eh ti khaw a thui pah (5.1-11). Hekah capat he AD 50-54 tluk vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Kuttuk nah \ior (1. 1-3)\ior*
\io1 Pathen a ngaih khosaknah \ior (1. 4—3. 13)\ior*
\io1 Pathen kongaih la khosaknah \ior (4. 1-12)\ior*
\io1 Khrih koep halonah kawng \ior (4. 13—5. 11)\ior*
\io1 Phihnah neh uentonah \ior (5. 12-28)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Toidalnah
\p 
